						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/the-old-current-a-poem-by-brad-leithauser/">
				<h4 style="margin:0">“The Old Current,” a Poem by Brad Leithauser</h4>
			</a>
			A gritty bench, a grubby river,
And an ongoing wave of wonderment:
How capable and amazing
Everything is, such people...			
